<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:15:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾 8 月出口订单超出预期，人工智能需求强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-august-export-orders-beat-forecasts-solid-demand-ai-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于人工智能（AI）应用芯片的需求持续攀升，台湾 8 月份的出口订单超出预期，政府预计这一强劲势头将延续到今年剩余时间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-august-export-orders-beat-forecasts-solid-demand-ai-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国调查美国PVH公司涉嫌抵制新疆产品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-probes-us-firm-pvh-over-suspected-boycotting-xinjiang-products-2024-09-24/</link><description>商务部周二表示，中国将对 Calvin Klein 和 Tommy Hilfiger 的母公司 PVH 涉嫌违反涉疆产品市场交易原则进行调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 08:31:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-probes-us-firm-pvh-over-suspected-boycotting-xinjiang-products-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激措施推动欧洲股市上涨；奢侈品股大放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-jump-china-stimulus-luxury-stocks-shine-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于中国全面的刺激措施提振了奢侈品公司和矿业公司的股票，欧洲股市周二上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:45:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-jump-china-stimulus-luxury-stocks-shine-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激措施提振矿业和奢侈品股，伦敦股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-shares-jump-china-stimulus-lifts-mining-luxury-stocks-2024-09-24/</link><description>英国股市周二跟随全球涨幅上涨，因市场对中国新的刺激措施表示欢迎，这些措施提振了矿业公司和专注于奢侈品的零售商的股价。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/london-shares-jump-china-stimulus-lifts-mining-luxury-stocks-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国零跑汽车和Stellantis在欧洲开放廉价电动汽车订单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-stellantis-open-orders-europe-budget-evs-2024-09-24/</link><description>周二，中国零跑汽车及其合作伙伴 Stellantis 表示，该公司将开始在欧洲接受一款城市轿车和一款 SUV 的订单，以扩大其在该地区的廉价电动汽车 (EV) 产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-stellantis-open-orders-europe-budget-evs-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称中国是俄罗斯武器外国技术的主要途径</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-china-is-key-route-foreign-tech-russian-weapons-2024-09-24/</link><description>乌克兰总统顾问弗拉迪斯拉夫·弗拉休克周二对记者表示，在乌克兰战场上发现的俄罗斯武器中大约60%的外国零部件来自中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:25:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-china-is-key-route-foreign-tech-russian-weapons-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>卢比停止连涨，远期升水维持在 18 个月高位附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-halts-winning-streak-forward-premiums-hold-near-18-month-high-2024-09-24/</link><description>由于进口商通常以美元付款，印度卢比的涨势将于周二停止，而在美联储官员发表鸽派言论后，远期升水保持在数月高位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/rupee-halts-winning-streak-forward-premiums-hold-near-18-month-high-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>受伤的拉杜卡努成为最新退出中国公开赛的大牌球员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-raducanu-latest-big-name-pull-out-china-open-2024-09-24/</link><description>Elena Rybakina、Iga Swiatek 和 Ons Jabeur 也将缺席北京的比赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 06:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/injured-raducanu-latest-big-name-pull-out-china-open-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲高级官员表示摩根大通看好印度和日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jpmorgan-bullish-india-japan-top-asia-official-says-2024-09-24/</link><description>美国最大银行摩根大通一位高级官员表示，看好亚洲的印度和日本，但也热衷于将资源配置到受益于“中国加一”战略的东南亚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:48:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/jpmorgan-bullish-india-japan-top-asia-official-says-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出大范围降息和其他刺激措施以刺激疲软的经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rolls-out-broad-rate-cuts-other-stimulus-spur-weak-economy-2024-09-24/</link><description>中国周二宣布了一系列广泛的刺激措施，以支持步履蹒跚的经济、稳定房地产业并恢复市场信心。消息公布后，股票和债券大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rolls-out-broad-rate-cuts-other-stimulus-spur-weak-economy-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>G7表示中东局势升级不会给任何人带来好处</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-says-nobody-will-gain-middle-east-escalation-2024-09-24/</link><description>七国集团（G7）主要民主国家的外交部长周一警告称，在中东的行动和反行动有可能将该地区拖入一场更广泛的冲突，而任何国家都不会从中受益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:47:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-says-nobody-will-gain-middle-east-escalation-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：没有火箭筒，但中国最新的刺激措施让人松了一口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-24/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:38:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>Interax报道称，俄罗斯和中国军舰进入鄂霍次克海进行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russia-china-warships-enter-sea-okhotsk-drills-interax-reports-2024-09-24/</link><description>俄罗斯国际文传电讯社周二援引太平洋舰队新闻部门的消息称，作为海军联合演习的一部分，俄罗斯太平洋舰队和中国海军的一支军舰编队进入西太平洋鄂霍次克海。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 04:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/russia-china-warships-enter-sea-okhotsk-drills-interax-reports-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行推出疫情以来最激进刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-broad-stimulus-measures-revive-economy-2024-09-24/</link><description>央行将把银行必须持有的现金储备量削减50个基点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 03:36:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-broad-stimulus-measures-revive-economy-2024-09-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国坚定支持黎巴嫩维护安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-firmly-supports-lebanon-safeguarding-its-security-2024-09-24/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一向黎巴嫩外长布哈比卜表示，中方坚定支持黎巴嫩维护主权和安全，强烈谴责以色列大规模空袭后的违法行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 03:01:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-firmly-supports-lebanon-safeguarding-its-security-2024-09-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>